Enum Constant Detail

SubSampling

public static final Sampling SubSampling
Implements regular sub sampling without replacement. This method cannot return samples that are larger than the original data set.

NormalBootstrapping

public static final Sampling NormalBootstrapping
Implements normal bootstrapping. This amounts to sub sampling with replacement.
